| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0781 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17c4e063-e5e4-5f8a-9edd-732b69454dd9"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
